parameters:
Imperial Secret Agent Amina: Thank you for coming to us with
such a request.

Clea: I'm sorry, but I still don't trust you. I'll keep my
weapon ready, if you don't mind.

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: I understand your skepticism...
The request is to free Luid from Queen Caron's curse.

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: Please bear with me for a
little while as I share my past story with you.
Clea: So Luid is Queen Caron's biological child...

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: Caron is using that to her
advantage, brainwashing him... That is not true love...!

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: Please, I beg you to cooperate!
I alone cannot reach him, I cannot sway Luid's heart--

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: You've noticed...! Everyone,
please run away. It's my responsibility!

Clea: I have decided to formally accept your request. I can
see your desperation is genuine.

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: The production of the Eratoma
Dragon has entered its final stage.

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: All of this is due to Queen
Caron's suspicion and fear. She doubts and suspects
everything, even the Imperial Secret Agents who are her
pawns.

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: I don't have a complete grasp
of the situation, but it seems they are conducting research
to create monsters other than dragons.

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: Will this be the reward for
accepting the request?

Clea: The reward is more than enough. Where exactly is Mr.
Luid?
Priestess Sophia: ...So Oros was the meeting place, huh?
Thief Nora: Um, what do you mean?

Mage Relm: Oros is Prince Lex's base. Is Mr. Luid working on
a defection plan?

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: As you have said, I am aware of
your master's negotiation destination, so I will guide you.

Imperial Secret Agent Amina: Master... I mean, please take
care of Luid.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
